sleeping...

\N<\N[2]>Ah, welcome back♪...You must be tired, staying in the
dungeon until this time of morning?

\N<Luna>Uh, um... Yeah, that's right~ I was on a roll, so I kept on
dungeon-crawling and before I knew it, it got this late~...

Luna, in order to prevent \N[2] from realizing the arrest
and gang rape that occurred in the slums, pretended she was
just returning from the dungeon

\N<\N[2]>By the way, there seems to have been an incident in the
slums, something about a criminal escaping~ It's been the
talk of the village~ But I guess Luna-chan wouldn't know
since you were dungeon diving

\N<\N[2]>The slums really are dangerous, huh~ Even though we're
adventurers, I think we should avoid going there carelessly

\N<Luna>Oh really~ (sweat) I had no idea that happened~ You're right
\N[2]-kun, we should stay away from the slums as much as
possible~ (I can't possibly tell him that I'm actually the
culprit)

\N<\N[2]>That's for the best... Well then, I'm off to the dungeon. I
want to get back to our normal lives as soon as possible♪

\N<Luna>Right, take care... I'm a bit tired so I'll take a break for
a while

Luna was relieved that \N[2] hadn't noticed anything for the
moment, but as soon as she let her guard down, the fatigue
from her previous nightmare overwhelmed her and everything
went dark before her eyes

\N<\N[2]>Good morning♪ I'll do my best hunting monsters even if it's
just me!

\N<\N[2]>Ah, good work today! It was pretty decent... We've got to
keep our spirits up and do our best tomorrow too~
Will you sleep until the next morning?

door... Good night♪

front door opens.

And then, those footsteps head towards Luna's bed where she
is sleeping...

About the "Two Systems" and "Clock" on the Menu Screen

～Debt Repayment System～(1/2) The number displayed is your
current \C[2]debt balance\C[0]. You can make payments
through the \C[3]Send Money button\C[0]. Once the displayed
amount reaches \C[17]0G\C[0], you have \C[14]cleared the
game\C[0].

～SNS System～(2/2) Not only Luna and her friends, but also
other adventurers carry devices. Use the \C[31]camera
function\C[0] on these devices to check what kind of posts
adventurers make on the lawless SNS of the frontier.

～Clock System～ Clicking on the clock will advance time by
\C[2]1 hour\C[0]. Please use it for time-limited events and
such.

Beyond this point is the \C[3]ending\C[0]. Please proceed if
you wish to clear the game.
